Description: port window and audio to SDL2
 Replace the X11/GLX window (glwindow.cpp) and the OSS/ALSA audio drivers
 (linux_oss.cpp, linux_alsa.cpp) with SDL2 equivalents.
 .
 SDL2 handles window creation, OpenGL context, event loop and audio output,
 removing the dependencies on libX11, libXxf86vm, libXext and libasound2.
